<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1008,1218,1243]" box="[151,1008,1218,1243]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
The original description of 
<taxonomicName box="[457,607,1219,1243]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Apis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="meriana">
<emphasis box="[457,607,1219,1243]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Apis meriana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Olivier" box="[649,852,1218,1242]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Olivier, G. A. (1789) Abeille. In: G. A. Olivier (Ed.), [Encyclopedie methodique, ou par ordre de matieres; par une societe de gens de lettres, de savants et d'artistes] Encyclopedie methodique, histoire naturelle, insectes. Panckoucke, Plomteux, Paris &amp; Liege, pp. 46 - 84." type="book chapter" year="1789">
Olivier (
<number box="[744,805,1218,1242]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1789.0">1789</number>
: 
<number box="[815,844,1218,1242]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="64.0">64</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
is as follows:
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[199,1437,1290,1589]" box="[199,364,1290,1312]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">“Abeille Mérian</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[199,1437,1290,1589]" box="[199,401,1321,1343]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<taxonomicName authority="Meriana. Nob." authorityName="Meriana. Nob." box="[199,401,1321,1343]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Apis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[199,337,1322,1343]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Apis Meriana</emphasis>
